name: WKNavigationResponse
desc: An object that contains the response to a navigation request, and which you use to make navigation-related policy decisions.

items.name: var canShowMIMEType: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether WebKit is capable of displaying the response’s MIME type natively.

items.name: var isForMainFrame: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the response targets the web view’s main frame.
